metadata.name: Your COLLΞCTIPOD is waiting for you!
metadata.description:
Your COLLΞCTIPOD can't wait to be revealed and meet you!

The COLLΞCTIPODZ is a collection of 9696 unique, detail-based, ethereum-inspired, and algorithmically generated crypto capsules from over 96+ traits.

Each capsule descending to the metaverse is unique, but specific traits make some units rarer than others. Ownership of a COLLΞCTIPOD will also grant you access to additional benefits which will be revealed over time.
